tyle=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 13px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">We have business jobs in a variety of fields. If you are interested in banking, accounting, or finance, you will be happy with the large number of jobs available. We have entry-level positions for recent high school graduates and executive positions as chief financial officers. We also have jobs for everything in between. If you have a high school diploma or a masters degree, we can help you find business jobs now.</p><p data-mce-style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; margin-left: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #262626; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 13px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Management jobs in human resources allow you to take part in the personnel issues of a company. In this position, you will often screen, interview, and hire staff. You may also design salary and benefit packages, oversee retirement plans, and create training programs. Administrative support personnel are also needed to work in the human relations field.</p><p data-mce-style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; margin-left: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #262626; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 13px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">If marketing is your dream, check out our extensive list of business jobs available for you. We can guide you to jobs in advertising, public relations, market research, product management, and retail. There are many career choices when it comes to working in marketing.</p><p data-mce-style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; margin-left: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #262626; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 13px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Within other careers are business jobs. Healthcare cannot function without a qualified administrative staff. Work at the front desk or insurance office of a physicians office or become the administrator or a large hospital.</p><p data-mce-style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; margin-left: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #262626; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 13px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><br></p><p data-mce-style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; margin-left: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #262626; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 13px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">The hospitality industry needs personnel to handle their billing, planning, advertising, and numerous other functions. Jobs may be in hotels, restaurants, in resorts, and on cruise ships. These jobs can be found locally or they can take you around the world.</p><p data-mce-style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; margin-left: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #262626; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 13px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Since the career path is so wide, the salary for all business jobs varies greatly. As with most other jobs, salary is largely dependent upon education, training, and scope of the job. Entry level jobs may pay slightly over minimum wage while top executive can earn in excess of $1,000,000 per year. Most business jobs pay in between those two extremes. A career in business is a smart move. It can take you from one career to another.</p><p data-mce-style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; margin-left: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #262626; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 13px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Secretaries and administrative assistants are always in demand. Individuals with some computer-related experience have better opportunities. The median annual salary for all secretaries is $36,000. Legal and medical secretaries typically earn substantially more.</p><p data-mce-style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; margin-left: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: #262626; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; margin-left: 0px; font-size: 13px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">We have business jobs available now for qualified individuals. Whether you are just entering the workforce or looking to move up to a new and exciting position, we may have just what you are looking for. Spend some time perusing the large number of jobs we have available. Check out the employers who are seeking for competent applicants. If you require any assistance applying for these business jobs, let us know. It is our mission to match up qualified job seekers with the best job possible.</p>', 4, 1, 'income,expense,account,accounting', 2, '2023-09-18', '2053-09-18', 'active', 'gender,dob,country', 'profile,resume,letter,terms', '65585155ac2d4', '1,2,3', 6, '2023-11-18 05:53:25', '2023-11-18 05:53:25');
